OL,3,C'Vulnerable' estate residents told not
OL,4,Cto drink tap water after bacteria found
OL,6,FIt has been one week since people
OL,7,Fliving on a Cheltenham housing estate
OL,8,Fwere told not to drink their tap water
OL,9,Fafter tests one week ago found the
OL,10,Fpresence of bacteria in the supply.
OL,12,FOne pensioner told ITV News it is a
OL,13,F'worry' for her and her husband who is
OL,14,Frequired to take medication on a daily
OL,15,Fbasis and 'won't leave the house'.
OL,17,FInvestigations are continuing into the
OL,18,Fwater systems for households on Barlow
OL,19,FRoad in Hester's Way, which have been
OL,20,Fprovided with bottled water.
