OL,3,C'Vulnerable' estate residents told not
OL,4,Cto drink tap water after bacteria found
OL,6,FAll 75 flats were impacted, with
OL,7,Fresidents, some of whom are elderly
OL,8,Fand vulnerable, advised to not drink
OL,9,Ftap water or use it to brush their
OL,10,Fteeth.
OL,12,FTenants were also warned against
OL,13,Fletting water enter their mouths when
OL,14,Fwashing or having a shower.
OL,16,FOne resident described "strong brown"
OL,17,Fwater coming out of his taps.
OL,19,FAnother said: "It's a bit of a
OL,20,Fnuisance. At first, it was a bit of a
OL,21,Fworry because my husband is 86.
