OL,3,C'Vulnerable' estate residents told not
OL,4,Cto drink tap water after bacteria found
OL,6,F"We're both vulnerable, we've both got
OL,7,Fa lot of medication we take. And he
OL,8,Fwon't go out the house, so this just
OL,9,Fmakes him worse really."
OL,11,FAnother added: "They haven't really
OL,12,Fsaid much, we've just got to have
OL,13,Fbottled water until further notice."
OL,15,FCheltenham Borough Council manages the
OL,16,Fhomes and is leading the investigation.
