OL,3,C'Vulnerable' estate residents told not
OL,4,Cto drink tap water after bacteria found
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "Tests that have
OL,7,Fbeen carried out as part of an ongoing
OL,8,Finvestigation at some of the
OL,9,Fproperties on Barlow Road are starting
OL,10,Fto come back. So far these are showing
OL,11,Fup as clear.
OL,13,F"This is great news, as this means
OL,14,Fthat those properties aren't affected
OL,15,Fso can now access their water supply.
OL,16,FWe will be liaising with these tenants
OL,17,Ftoday.
