OL,3,C'Vulnerable' estate residents told not
OL,4,Cto drink tap water after bacteria found
OL,6,F"For the remaining tenants we will
OL,7,Fcontinue to work with our partner
OL,8,Fagencies to carry out testing and
OL,9,Fawait for the remaining results. We
OL,10,Fwill keep our tenants informed and
OL,11,Fupdated on any changes.
OL,13,F"We are continuing to talk with
OL,14,Ftenants, provide advice and carry out
OL,15,Fwelfare checks. Staff will remain
OL,16,Fonsite to provide bottled water and
OL,17,Fprovide support until the situation is
OL,18,Fresolved."
