OL,3,C'Vulnerable' estate residents told not
OL,4,Cto drink tap water after bacteria found
OL,6,FCabinet Member for Housing Cllr Flo
OL,7,FClucas explained: "All over this bank
OL,8,Fholiday weekend - and I thank them
OL,9,Ffrom the bottom of my heart for doing
OL,10,Fit - officers have been working, not
OL,11,Fon holiday.
OL,13,F"They've been in here, they've been
OL,14,Fgiving people bottled water. All of
OL,15,Fthe flats are being tested."
OL,17,FSevern Trent is supporting the council
OL,18,Fand has assured the public that the
OL,19,Fbacteria is not a wider issue on the
OL,20,Fnetwork.
